element hunters (エレメントハンター eremento hantā, hangul: 엘리먼트 헌터; rr: elimeonteu heonteo) is a 2009 anime series that began airing in japan and korea as a science-fiction adventure to generate more awareness in chemistry and other sciences. a manga series began at the same time, and has continued even after the anime ended in 2010. bandai has released a nintendo ds game for element hunters, it was released on october 22, 2009 in japan.